01:07:47.580 --> 01:07:49.930
It was my first time
of participating

01:07:49.930 --> 01:07:51.880
in the International
Writing Program.

01:07:51.880 --> 01:07:55.070
And I was very lucky
to return this year,

01:07:55.070 --> 01:07:57.360
thanks to the [inaudible]
College,

01:07:57.360 --> 01:08:01.630
which is like one hour
away from Iowa city.

01:08:01.630 --> 01:08:05.880
And it's a fascinating
phenomenon, the juncture

01:08:05.880 --> 01:08:10.910
of two lifestyles,
farmers, agricultural,

01:08:10.910 --> 01:08:15.080
traditional lifestyle
