01:08:30.160 --> 01:08:34.620
And, also, it was -- I was --

01:08:34.620 --> 01:08:37.290
it was curious to talk to
my driver, because I try

01:08:37.290 --> 01:08:38.770
to [inaudible] every week, or --

01:08:38.770 --> 01:08:42.080
