a man who voted for Trump,

01:08:42.080 --> 01:08:48.010
and it was really interesting to
hear -- to hear his arguments.

01:08:48.010 --> 01:08:54.330
And it was a big contrast
with what is generally thought

01:08:54.330 --> 01:08:58.480
in campuses, or in Iowa city.

01:08:58.480 --> 01:09:01.490
It's beautiful that you
have all these voices

01:09:01.490 --> 01:09:06.090
and all these diversities,
and I would love

01:09:06.090 --> 01:09:09.810
to come back someday,
