01:09:11.950 --> 01:09:13.250
&gt;&gt; Rumena Ruzarovska: I don't
know if it's going to --

01:09:13.250 --> 01:09:14.710
it hasn't appeared
in my writing yet,

01:09:14.710 --> 01:09:17.020
but this is where I
